<description>&lt;div class="pageBefore">&lt;img src="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/images/z.gif" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="display:block" align="top" />&lt;/div>&lt;div class="page">
&lt;b>Сравнение версий &lt;a  href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RazdelTariffs/FormaRateGroups&amp;amp;v=svr" class="">/Документация&amp;nbsp;IP&amp;nbsp;Studio&amp;nbsp;AMBS&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;Раздел&amp;nbsp;Tariffs&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;Форма&amp;nbsp;Rate&amp;nbsp;Groups&lt;/a> за &lt;a href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RazdelTariffs/FormaRateGroups&amp;amp;time=2007-03-03+13%3A25%3A33">2007-03-03 13:25:33&lt;/a> и &lt;a href="http://78.46.73.113/wiki/wakka.php?wakka=DokumentacijaIPStudioAMBS/RazdelTariffs/FormaRateGroups&amp;amp;time=2007-03-03+13%3A26%3A17">2007-03-03 13:26:17&lt;/a>&lt;/b>&lt;br />
